ts per day, this was the ceiling. At 35 minutes per heat, 41 heats per day became achievable."}),(0,p.jsx)("div",{className:"case-image-single",children:(0,p.jsx)(f,{src:"/images/metalcloud/spectro-opportunity.png",alt:"Radar chart showing impact on Production Cost, Energy Loss, Time, and Productivity — with 36 vs 41 heats per day comparison",className:"case-visual"})}),(0,p.jsx)("p",{className:"opportunity-highlight",children:"Opportunity: 20% cost saving (approx)"}),(0,p.jsxs)("p",{className:"opportunity-dimensions",children:[(0,p.jsx)("strong",{children:"4 dimensions of impact:"})," Production Cost · Energy Loss · Time · Productivity"]})]}),(0,p.jsxs)("div",{className:"opportunity-block",children:[(0,p.jsx)("h3",{children:"OPTIMISE"}),(0,p.jsx)("p",{children:"Three pain points discovered through user interviews:"}),(0,p.jsxs)("ol",{children:[(0,p.jsx)("li",{children:"Raw material price is not considered while creating ChargeMix"}),(0,p.jsx)("li",{children:"Manual calculations introduce human errors"}),(0,p.jsx)("li",{children:"Multiple experimental heats are run when the mix is wrong — each one costs money"})]}),(0,p.jsx)("div",{className:"case-image-single",children:(0,p.jsx)(f,{src:"/images/metalcloud/optimise-painpoints.png",alt:"Optimise — 12% cost saving opportunity identified through pain point analysis",className:"case-visual"})}),(0,p.jsx)("p",{className:"opportunity-highlight",children:"Opportunity: 12% cost saving (approx)"})]})]})]})}),(0,p.jsx)("section",{className:"case-section case-section--surface fade-up",children:(0,p.jsxs)("div",{className:"case-section__inner",children:[(0,p.jsx)("h2",{children:"Connected. Calculated. Delivered."}),(0,p.jsxs)("div",{className:"solution-subsection",children:[(0,p.jsx)("h3",{children:"Spectro Pro — what we built"}),(0,p.jsxs)("div",{children:[(0,p.jsx)("p",{children:"The solution had 4 components working together:"}),(0,p.jsxs)("ol",{className:"solution-list",children:[(0,p.jsxs)("li",{children:[(0,p.jsx)("strong